<para>Constant true. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Indicates that the device driver supports 64 bit integers shader resource types. <simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="struct_device_driver_capabilities_base_1af3cfbb31804f081b404e6c40b51597e8" kindref="member">DeviceDriverCapabilitiesBase::hasShader64BitIntegerResources</ref> </para>
